comments.raw_text:
@Alex: you are right!
Apparently if you had status-4-evar installed once upon a time, even if completely removed before installing anything else, it is broken. A factory-profile doesn't display this behavior. Since I didn't have anything else installed add-on wise when I wrote this bug, the STR didn't include this.

The fact that it can end up in any location but the end of the bar is, IMO, a problem; it should probably be forced in it's correct spot at all times.

